{"tid":1305080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋對警犬出翻份聲明有無得諗？","createTime":"2019-07-10T18:50:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T18:50:36.000Z","uid":35994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"98508d2c9360fd88d6e756687cd67c1f4d9530f0","tid":1305080,"uid":35994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:50:36.000Z","msg":"突然間諗起，不如我哋對香港警察出份聲明<br />\n<br />\n大慨講話對佢哋行為極度不滿，然後<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">俾一個限期佢哋，呼籲有良知嘅警察即時辭職</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果唔辭職就當一般警犬無異，日後有何後果自己承擔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n當然呢份聲明，唔係真係希望有警犬會辭職啦，要辭都一早辭左啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">旨在令日後做乜都叫出師有個名，唔洗啲和理非話咩仲有啲有良知嘅警察</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有無得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}